<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4468217>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 9–18. Pentacomia (Mesochila) skrabali sp. nov. from type locality. 9 – head, HT (USNM). 10–11 – male labrum: 10 – HT; 11 – PT (DBCN). 12–13 – female labrum: 12 – AT (NHMK); 13 – PT (DBCN). 14–15 – pronotum: 14 – male, HT; 15 – female, PT (DDCP). 16–18 – elytron: 16 – male, HT; 17 – female, AT; 18 – female, PT (DDCP). Bars = 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4468217/files/figure.png" .

